{"tid":623814,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人一做Presentation就好易面都紅撚晒？","createTime":"2018-04-10T09:52:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T13:25:32.000Z","uid":155344,"like":59,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"89345f46bdb27fd2b2774410cdcceb29f41d9a47","tid":623814,"uid":155344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T09:52:44.000Z","msg":"由細到大都好易面紅<br />\n到依家二十幾歲人 做咗嘢幾年<br />\n一開會要對住好多人講嘢 或者做Presentation<br />\n都好撚易面紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅到好似腦衝血咁 唔知做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實有冇方法可以解決？<br />\n唔想成日比人笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7093eb7d224fedbb50c8d089329ea215c46cef93","tid":623814,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T09:58:15.000Z","msg":"渣ga--"},{"pid":"e3ade337b21b0e551f19aaa072e4fa66fca3c502","tid":623814,"uid":64944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"me<br />\n我仲撚慘 已經做緊野"},{"pid":"798f31f712bc90c809ddf41fa5c467cede5b4539","tid":623814,"uid":34189,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:00:41.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個到中學答問題,出去講野就面紅,成身都熱曬流埋汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n到左大學就好D,唔會咁易面紅<br />\n除非up錯野/比人問到唔識答"},{"pid":"ead6afd289ac32e3fe027749fb770afca1330d71","tid":623814,"uid":176903,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:03:27.000Z","msg":"我試過紅撚到連個龜頭都充曬血<br />\n比人望住晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a29ff5a73e9ed239f088a2f99a96696641e16638","tid":623814,"uid":74380,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:04:31.000Z","msg":"緊張係正常架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"662ff2e861c09f8f8fb73216a76134a5db249082","tid":623814,"uid":36372,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:10:09.000Z","msg":"我會幾秒內紅晒 跟住十秒內退返"},{"pid":"9c7bcc1f086c280a7a9b2a171c93ef4a97225f5a","tid":623814,"uid":42469,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:12:02.000Z","msg":"你通頂prepare PowerPoint slides，present個陣就無心情理台下諗乜，只想返屋企訓覺"},{"pid":"c158f9a348e20df127948f255c3adf8df5be50c3","tid":623814,"uid":152262,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:12:57.000Z","msg":"Present 前扮猩猩"},{"pid":"4a67c272dccc34ae88d4dd3d85dd2b07a525c7e5","tid":623814,"uid":176114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:13:52.000Z","msg":"中學嗰陣一答問題或者出去講野都會臉紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 解決辦法就係開大個冷氣或者風扇降温<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到宜家大學，多左出去present就好左好多，冇臉紅，可能慣左或者身邊有fd就ok啲，但問問題都feel到紅左，只係冇中學咁嚴重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cd4f5a886a6bd60efa0acfe84d8f14529287a5","tid":623814,"uid":112416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"做左十年野<br />\n<br />\n臉紅<br />\n耳紅<br />\n眼鏡有霧氣<br />\n額頭有汗"},{"pid":"e3dd72478a084003062159dcf309ee798045c530","tid":623814,"uid":176114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T10:15:44.000Z","msg":"試下開會前開大個冷氣令自己凍啲，可以嘅話唔好著褸"},{"pid":"9f1705250aa7e4dfdba0512305091f7b28ba98da","tid":623814,"uid":61105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T11:48:07.000Z","msg":"見工都係咁，成日被人問係咪冷氣唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p