 人以為我怕醜但其實我只係諗緊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4de64aac50b664e9143ad05d9e5612ab1f0d9752","tid":623814,"uid":3932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:23:21.000Z","msg":"我都係 好大困擾"},{"pid":"42c9b7db94535d3b4512faf64723b7691f9de495","tid":623814,"uid":71496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:25:47.000Z","msg":"求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bcccc9d49d763cbbf83c487e8d1b348a3969d2e","tid":623814,"uid":23445,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:50:10.000Z","msg":"頭1分鐘會面紅+口疾疾<br />\n但會愈講愈順,同埋冷靜返<br />\n<br />\n所以一開頭通常都9up下<br />\n重要野係尾段先講"},{"pid":"261c8efb32a98ed06757cbf6d50a3a5466c3f362","tid":623814,"uid":147770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T12:56:06.000Z","msg":"Present冇問題 唔好注視住我就得"},{"pid":"549ac1ae930869c22079ef4655945de4b6860d15","tid":623814,"uid":155344,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-10T14:11:15.000Z","msg":"成日比人問我做咩面紅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一問完我塊面就仲紅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個隻紅仲要係久久不散個隻<br />\n有時笑得激動d都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩方法可以練到唔面紅 講大話都好易比人知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}